{{Italic title}} '''''Pugh's Almanac''''' was an annual [[almanac]] published in [[Queensland]], [[Australia]]. It provided a guide to Queensland, and information about the events of the previous year and included several directories of commercial and non-commercial organisations.<ref name=tq>{{cite web|title=Pugh's Almanac|url=http://www.textqueensland.com.au/pughs-almanac|website=Text Queensland|accessdate=13 June 2014}}</ref> ==History== It was founded by [[Theophilus Parsons Pugh]], and published from 1859-1927.<ref name=tq/>
